                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="14409241" author="joerg@j-hohwiller.de" created="Fri, 28 Oct 2005 12:47:56 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Sorry, typoo. I meant&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://svn.projxpert.com/mmm/trunk/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://svn.projxpert.com/mmm/trunk/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14409220" author="elpunzalan" created="Tue, 8 Nov 2005 00:46:33 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi, the cause of the infinite loop is not the depth of the project and/or the modules in it.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Look in the ui-toolkit/subproject/swing/pom.xml and you&apos;ll see that the project has the same artifactId as the parent.  That is what&apos;s causing the infinite loop.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14409338" author="elpunzalan" created="Tue, 8 Nov 2005 02:06:04 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m attaching a fix to prevent the infinite loop and also improve the validation of the project descriptor.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14420398" author="joerg@j-hohwiller.de" created="Wed, 9 Nov 2005 16:32:12 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;You are so right. Thanks for that. Would be nice if maven would detect this and given a more precise error message.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14409390" author="elpunzalan" created="Wed, 9 Nov 2005 17:55:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The attached path would do that.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14409552" author="jdcasey" created="Tue, 6 Dec 2005 10:53:10 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Applied patch, with small logic fix: was comparing parent.getGroupId() to pom.getArtifactId(), instead of comparing groupId&apos;s in the DefaultModelValidator.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17996869" author="JIRAUSER302100" created="Sat, 5 Jul 2025 08:32:53 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This project has moved from Jira to GitHub Issues. This issue was migrated to &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/maven/issues/3565&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;apache/maven#3565&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
